Now, I need to identify the product in the current compare list and add the Pre-baked Gingerbread House Kit to it. However, the current state of the page does not show the specific product in the compare list, so I need to add the product manually. I will use the search function to find the Pre-baked Gingerbread House Kit and then add it to the compare list.
